becau&s;e abundance of Ladies pa&s;s
thro' their hands; and it was under
this Sanctify'd Habit, the Count <HI>de</HI>
&mdash;Dragoon'd the other Night,
the Counte&s;s <HI>of the Green;</HI> whom he
